  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Mokuton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 6</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 19 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 7 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 20</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique can only affect an area of (very) soft or firm ground. Vines and bushes burst from the ground, entangling creatures in the area. Such creates can make a Strength check or Escape Artist check (DC 20) to move up to half their normal speed as a full-round action. If a creature moves out of the area, it is no longer entangled and is no longer restrained in their movements. Creatures that make their save are not entangled but can still only move at half their speed, and cannot run or charge, while inside the area.<br><br>Each round on your turn, creatures in the area that aren't entangled by this technique must make a new save or become @Condition[entangled]{entangled} as above.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
